  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the curry powder and turmeric and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the apricots and cook until they start to soften, about 3 minutes.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, until the apricots are tender, about 10 minutes.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve hot over rice or with naan bread."
